org.activebpel.rt.axis
Class AeMutableServiceDesc

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.axis.AeServiceDesc
      org.activebpel.rt.axis.AeMutableServiceDesc
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, org.apache.axis.description.ServiceDesc
public class AeMutableServiceDesc
extends AeServiceDesc

A ServiceDesc impl that delegates access to its wsdl related properties to an IAeWsdlReference. This allows the wsdl reference to cache/update its properties as the catalog is updated.
